Old Stones

The land known as Old Stones is steeped in magic and mystery. Located to the west of the mainlands of Miravalis, this region encapsulates a large portion of the continent, and varies in terrain. One thing is for certain, though, the Old Stones is a place of immense magical power. Some take this as a blessing, others see it as a challenge. Some even rumor that the Old Stones is the ground zero for all magic that spreads throughout Miravalis, and is home to many unexplained ancient architectural mysteries that rivals even Earth's pyramids.

Magic flows freely here, and all know better than to trifle with the land. The great forest in the Northwest, named The Forest Unyielding, is home to all manner of magical entity. No less than 9 druidic sects patrol the forest and safeguard its mysteries. It is said that the trees have been known to speak to the perceptive, and there are beasts who are as smart as humans. The mountains at the northernmost tip of Old Stones are harsh places of great power. There are an uncounted many mage fortresses and secret halls hidden in the peaks and valleys. Some, who are especially wise or especially foolish, whisper that the mountains themselves are alive, and simply waiting to rise again.
